00:08:18.731 --> 00:08:21.067
to hear our reporter, Miguel Marquez,

00:08:21.067 --> 00:08:22.435
who was talking about

00:08:22.435 --> 00:08:23.970
the protesters outside.

00:08:23.970 --> 00:08:25.671
Specifically, he was reporting on

00:08:25.671 --> 00:08:26.973
and showing,

00:08:26.973 --> 00:08:28.541
the American flag being lowered,

00:08:28.541 --> 00:08:30.810
the Palestinian flag being raised.

00:08:30.810 --> 00:08:33.646
We even saw some red triangles.

00:08:33.646 --> 00:08:35.081
we're showing it now.

00:08:35.081 --> 00:08:36.182
I don't know if you can see it,

00:08:36.182 --> 00:08:38.150
but we even saw some red triangles

00:08:38.150 --> 00:08:40.453
on some of the statues.

00:08:40.453 --> 00:08:42.121
what's your reaction to that?

00:08:42.121 --> 00:08:44.924
Well, I think it's it's disgraceful.

00:08:44.924 --> 00:08:46.425
It's, shameful

00:08:46.425 --> 00:08:48.060
and the kind of thing that we shouldn't

00:08:48.060 --> 00:08:48.761
see in this country.

00:08:48.761 --> 00:08:49.262
But again,

00:08:49.262 --> 00:08:51.063
as the Prime Minister pointed out

00:08:51.063 --> 00:08:52.899
today, a lot of these activities

00:08:52.899 --> 00:08:53.599
that are happening here

00:08:53.599 --> 00:08:54.333
in the United States,

00:08:54.333 --> 00:08:56.135
Iran is behind them.

00:08:56.135 --> 00:08:57.637
They are trying to create

00:08:57.637 --> 00:09:01.407
tumult and instability and chaos and,

00:09:01.741 --> 00:09:04.143
use in fueling all these protests

00:09:04.143 --> 00:09:05.578
and the violence, particularly

00:09:05.578 --> 00:09:06.712
the anti-Semitic violence

00:09:06.712 --> 00:09:07.980
in this country.

00:09:07.980 --> 00:09:09.615
that's Iranian activity.

00:09:09.615 --> 00:09:11.751
And that's why they have to be stopped,

00:09:11.751 --> 00:09:12.051
and that's

00:09:12.051 --> 00:09:12.852
why it's so important

00:09:12.852 --> 00:09:14.820
that we continue to support Israel,

00:09:14.820 --> 00:09:17.156
including, as the Prime minister said,

00:09:17.156 --> 00:09:18.591
give us the tools faster

00:09:18.591 --> 00:09:20.526
and we will finish the job.

00:09:20.526 --> 00:09:22.028
they've got to get this, this thing

00:09:22.028 --> 00:09:24.030
over with and,

00:09:24.030 --> 00:09:25.932
and send a clear statement to the world

00:09:25.932 --> 00:09:27.500
that this kind of behavior

00:09:27.500 --> 00:09:28.200
and the kind of thing

00:09:28.200 --> 00:09:29.602
that we're seeing right here in the U.S.

00:09:29.602 --> 00:09:31.671
and right here in this city today,

00:09:31.671 --> 00:09:33.205
just can't be tolerated.

00:09:33.205 --> 00:09:33.573
Senator,

00:09:33.573 --> 00:09:36.208
one of Prime Minister Netanyahu's

00:09:36.208 --> 00:09:38.411
predecessors, Ehud Barak,

00:09:38.411 --> 00:09:40.112
who we understand

00:09:40.112 --> 00:09:41.047
and we should tell our viewers

00:09:41.047 --> 00:09:41.714
who might not know,

00:09:41.714 --> 00:09:43.316
is not from the same party

00:09:43.316 --> 00:09:45.518
as Prime Minister Netanyahu.

00:09:45.518 --> 00:09:47.553
and but nonetheless, he has somebody he's

00:09:47.553 --> 00:09:49.689
somebody who has been intimately involved

00:09:49.689 --> 00:09:51.390
in trying to get to peace.

00:09:51.390 --> 00:09:52.858
He almost got there,

00:09:52.858 --> 00:09:53.559
when Bill Clinton

00:09:53.559 --> 00:09:54.093
had him

00:09:54.093 --> 00:09:55.728
and Yasser Arafat in 2000,

00:09:55.728 --> 00:09:57.330
here in the United States.

00:09:57.330 --> 00:09:57.997
He said

00:09:57.997 --> 00:09:59.599
very, very strongly

00:09:59.599 --> 00:10:01.901
and very clearly to Wolf,

00:10:01.901 --> 00:10:03.703
that he does not believe

00:10:03.703 --> 00:10:05.438
that Prime Minister Netanyahu

00:10:05.438 --> 00:10:07.039
actually wants to end the war

00:10:07.039 --> 00:10:08.341
because it would mean

00:10:08.341 --> 00:10:11.077
the end of his own political viability

00:10:11.077 --> 00:10:11.911
at home.

00:10:11.911 --> 00:10:13.479
And that might even mean,

00:10:13.479 --> 00:10:16.048
that hostages stay longer.

00:10:16.048 --> 00:10:17.750
Are you concerned about

00:10:17.750 --> 00:10:18.784
I mean, you're a politician.

00:10:18.784 --> 00:10:21.187
You understand what's going on in Israel?

00:10:21.187 --> 00:10:24.090
Are you concerned about the notion

00:10:24.090 --> 00:10:25.925
that Bibi Netanyahu

00:10:25.925 --> 00:10:26.859
isn't trying as hard

00:10:26.859 --> 00:10:30.663
as he can to get this deal because of

00:10:31.797 --> 00:10:34.467
his own concerns about his own future?

00:10:34.467 --> 00:10:35.434
I don't think that

00:10:35.434 --> 00:10:36.669
I've met with him in Israel.

00:10:36.669 --> 00:10:39.105
I've met with, Ehud Barak in Israel,

00:10:39.105 --> 00:10:40.206
previously as well.

00:10:40.206 --> 00:10:41.540
And obviously they have

00:10:41.540 --> 00:10:42.742
political differences there.

00:10:42.742 --> 00:10:44.310
But those aside,

00:10:44.310 --> 00:10:46.412
my sense coming out of this was is

00:10:46.412 --> 00:10:48.114
he is desperate to end this

00:10:48.114 --> 00:10:50.516
because this is putting the lives

00:10:50.516 --> 00:10:51.751
of Israeli citizens at

00:10:51.751 --> 00:10:53.352
risk every single day.

